CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 4, 1956, pg. A11, reads: "Future Socialites ... sons and daughters of Frogs smile at the success of their party Monday night for members of Pittsburgh's younger set. Chatting on the porch of Loendi Club are LaVerne Waddy, Bonnie Joy Waters, Connie Harris, Carolyn Waters and Grant Farmer. Bonnie was perhaps the youngest hostess there. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: LaVerne Waddy, Bonnie Joy Waters, Connie Harris, Carolyn Waters, and Grant Farmer wearing FROGS patches, gathered on Loendi Club porch for FROGS week event
